# CSS Engineering Guidelines

## Structure & Naming
- **BEM Methodology:**  
  - *Rule:* Name CSS classes using Block__Element--Modifier.  
  - *Why:* This ensures clarity and predictability in styling.
- **CSS Modules:**  
  - *Rule:* Use `.module.css` files for component-specific styles.  
  - *Why:* Prevents global leakage and simplifies maintenance.

